================================================================================
ADDITIONAL TERMS FOR NETWORK USE (AGPL Section 13)
================================================================================

If you modify this Program and make it available to users over a network,
you MUST make the complete corresponding source code available under the
terms of this license.

This requirement applies to:
  • SaaS platforms offering VariDex-based variant analysis
  • Cloud-hosted genomic interpretation services
  • Web-based ACMG classification tools using VariDex
  • API services that expose VariDex functionality to remote users
  • Any network-accessible service using modified VariDex code

You must provide:
  1. All source code for your modifications
  2. Build and installation instructions
  3. Any dependencies and configuration files
  4. A clear mechanism for users to download the complete source

For the full AGPL v3 license text, see:
https://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl-3.0.txt

